Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爾要遵守約定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.40,0:02:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.03,0:02:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 父親
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.28,0:02:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間還早吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你昨天受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.49,0:02:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼不多睡一會兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.46,0:02:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜很壯的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.73,0:02:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是身體 你有心事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.09,0:02:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是昨天被怪物襲擊的鎮民 以及…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.75,0:02:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「古物」消失前這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.16,0:02:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「爾要遵守約定」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.80,0:02:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次聽到「古物」開口說話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.51,0:02:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有「爾」指的是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.44,0:03:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「約定」又指的是?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們對小夜你來說是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.22,0:03:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是必須打敗的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.81,0:03:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能被「古物」怪物之語所迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽懂了麼 小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.93,0:03:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 父親
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四話 悲歎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天氣好晴朗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.53,0:03:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平時 都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.03,0:03:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼區別呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋蟬鳴泣聲聲繼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮雲未改外觀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情愉悅 人亦是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.01,0:03:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天氣好晴朗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:03:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平時 都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生活平穩亦如昔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.00,0:04:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心神寧靜不生波
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫柔善良的人們…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 一臉嚴肅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為我受了傷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.09,0:04:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須變得更強
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是一片祥和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.65,0:04:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣雖然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好像發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.94,0:04:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是麵包店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.42,0:04:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來 那兒還是沒開門呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果好像還是沒回來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.14,0:05:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.85,0:05:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早上過去的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽也是要去買麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻因此感到為難的人說的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.09,0:05:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實還沒回
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巡警都去Guimauve提醒注意了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.06,0:05:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察們也應該找過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.91,0:05:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 確實到處都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.81,0:05:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厭倦了這樣的鄉下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.46,0:05:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以離家出走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人不回家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也算離家出走麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還能怎麼說?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失蹤?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.95,0:05:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個詞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.09,0:05:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更衣同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有小狗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.64,0:05:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.12,0:06:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.63,0:06:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.32,0:06:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 先去醫務室
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.35,0:06:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.50,0:06:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.50,0:06:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 你幹嘛突然爬樹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.68,0:06:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在追東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.19,0:06:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狗 雖然我也不清楚是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是很小只
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.69,0:06:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼追狗追上樹了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那狗一下子就跳上了樹枝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是貓麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.69,0:07:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是狗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午飯 不快點吃的話午休就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.04,0:07:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時真同學你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.07,0:07:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飯還不如睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.05,0:07:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空著肚子 人也會沮喪的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.48,0:07:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 你之前也說過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.04,0:07:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.79,0:07:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.65,0:07:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時真你笑起來很帥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說…什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.52,0:08:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文人先生的便當很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文人先生是Guimauve咖啡廳的老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.35,0:08:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.31,0:08:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.23,0:08:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘗嘗飯團吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.05,0:08:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.25,0:08:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是你做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.73,0:08:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 文人先生做的被誇好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就覺得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫做文人的人 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜去哪兒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時真同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.81,0:09:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎樣的喜歡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.46,0:09:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很喜歡很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.63,0:09:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文人先生溫柔又會做菜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還一直聽我的碎碎念
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫柔又會做菜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能聽你說話 這樣就好了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是真的喜歡麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.00,0:09:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他那麼說了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:10:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是做了什麼惹時真同學生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.63,0:10:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒啦 我不那麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可他一直繃著臉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.99,0:10:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子也有很多原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.68,0:10:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他還很年輕嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然一喝文人先生的咖啡我就能平靜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那是為小夜做的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.47,0:10:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 Guimauve
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 小夜是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.19,0:10:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.24,0:11:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.17,0:11:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎麼就愣住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.51,0:11:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.47,0:11:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管發生什麼都要告訴我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.47,0:11:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論什麼小事 都一定要告訴我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.90,0:11:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.52,0:11:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變人的感情是很難的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.08,0:11:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是什麼樣的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.84,0:11:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要它已深深地刻在心中就很難改變
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最難改變的是憎惡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說仇恨不會持續
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.19,0:11:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但並不意味著仇恨會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.29,0:11:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是藏到了看不到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.47,0:11:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完好無損地保留著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.34,0:12:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且只要有一絲的機會 還會現形
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 如此難以對付的憎惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果無法消除該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終歸還是只能用同樣強烈的感情去覆蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須保護大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和憎惡同樣強烈的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.56,0:12:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是愛與信賴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和說好的不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然對肉體如此渴求
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消滅吾等的是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂戰術嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.42,0:17:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在操縱著那東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.99,0:17:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝等亦然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.47,0:17:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身在上位的人調度下面的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為欲調度別人之人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有所行動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.63,0:17:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然 有無法調度之物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.93,0:17:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需遵守約定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.23,0:17:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約…定?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Syujiki men
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs49.5}與「約定」有關的東西 目前尚無法確定是什麼 可能是「主事鬼面」「朱地鬼面」「取食免」等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Syujiki…?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.58,0:18:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等為自我而食
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.86,0:18:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝若阻撓 便連汝也吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有戰鬥才是應該做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.97,0:20:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.59,0:20:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.00,0:20:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.04,0:20:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.48,0:20:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過小夜沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.42,0:20:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「古物」也被消滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.66,0:20:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.83,0:20:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像和我們一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.56,0:20:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 又說了「要遵守約定」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求衛寧寧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.24,0:21:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.53,0:21:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求衛諾諾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.25,0:21:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.09,0:21:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我遲到了 　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.42,0:21:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 行的更衣同學已經點過了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.42,0:21:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs57}行：五十音圖的行 這裡表示排序 類似按英語字母順序或拼音順序排名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.73,0:21:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過名還沒點完 就放過你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.59,0:21:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天氣這麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.53,0:21:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒發生什麼騷亂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.45,0:21:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又會是美好平靜的一天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.40,0:23:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.96,0:23:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體育課中止 上自習
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.77,0:23:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼講鬼故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.31,0:23:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舉雙手贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.26,0:23:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自習時間可不是幹這種事情的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.33,0:23:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班長 不能害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.71,0:23:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪 哪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.19,0:23:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.96,0:24:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時真同學 不可以逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.28,0:24:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為要大家一起講恐怖的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.45,0:24:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話 BLood-C
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.63,0:24:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邂逅